====== H3974: מָאוֹר ======

===== Source =====

or   ; also (in plural) feminine   ; or   ; from  H215 ;

===== Meaning =====

properly, a  luminous  body or  luminary , i.e. (abstractly)  light  (as an element); figuratively,  brightness , i.e. cheerfulness ; specifically, a  chandelier

===== Definitions =====

  - luminous
  - luminary
  - light
  - brightness
  - cheerfulness
  - chandelier

===== Usage =====

bright, light.
